hrough multiple abstraction layers: HTTP endpoint → plugin manager → gRPC client → protobuf conversion → backend plugin execution → response marshaling to JSON. Data frames with typed fields and values are the core data structure that flows through this chain, being serialized from protobuf format back to JSON for HTTP response transmission."
